A Chrome extension enabling seamless conversation migration between ChatGPT and Claude — preserving context across LLM providers.

- Automatic auth token interception via the WebRequest API, paired with platform-specific content scripts for data extraction.
- Bidirectional conversion pipeline supporting conversation export, Markdown generation, and cross-platform import workflows.
